title: Keechaka audio released
text: The audio launch function of Keechaka was held recently in the city. The upcoming Telugu movie starring Jwala Koti and Raghubabu is said to be based on real life incidents. It has faced a tough time with the censor board to be passed with even an A certificate. The film features a total of 15 rape scenes pictured on the film's protagonist, a Keechaka, and his victims. Starting all with New comers, Keechaka is inspired from the story of a serial rapist in Nagpur who is said to have raped and even killed countless women and young girls.
